data.meta_description: His nickname was Big Ben. Ed was the son of James G. Bennett and Louisa (Lulu) Agnes McGrath. Ed attended Elm Vocational High School in Buffalo NY, and worked as a highway trooper and for Republic Steel Corporation. He married Helen Mahoney in the village of Angola NY on Feb. 4, 1934.
